Title: The Dissector Wakens
Description:
You are... not like the others...

I hear the Klaxxi calling... <cough>

I just need a moment.
ObjectivesText: Hold off the Zan'thik while Rik'kal wakens.
RewardText:
Look at you! Many parts and pieces... yes... and all of them so good at killing. Fascinating.

I must pick your brain some time. Muhahah.
